quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  33,7,"(Unibuke) ubwo twahaga abahanuzi isezerano rikomeye, ndetse nawe (Muhamadi), Nuhu, Ibrahimu, Musa, na Issa mwene Mariyamu. Kandi twabahaye isezerano rikomeye cyane"
  33,8,Kugira ngo (Allah) azabaze abanyakuri ibijyanye n’ukuri kwabo. Kandi yateganyirije abahakanyi ibihano bibabaza
  33,9,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimwibuke ingabire za Allah yabahundagajeho, ubwo ingabo zabateraga, tukazoherezamo umuyaga n’ingabo mutabonaga (Abamalayika). Kandi Allah ni Ubona bihebuje ibyo mukora"
  33,10,"Ubwo zabateraga zibaturutse haruguru no hepfo yanyu mukanuye amaso, imitima yabageze mu ngoto (kubera ubwoba), mutangiye gukekera Allah byinshi"
  33,11,"Aho abemera barahageragerejwe, banahindishwa umushyitsi ukomeye cyane"
  33,12,"(Unazirikane) ubwo indyarya n’abafite uburwayi mu mitima yabo (bwo gushidikanya) bavugaga bati \"Ibyo Allah n’Intumwa ye badusezeranyije ni ibinyoma"
  33,13,"Kandi (wibuke) igihe bamwe muri bo bavugaga bati \"Yemwe bantu ba Yathiribu (Madina)! Nta mpamvu yo kuba muri hano (murwana urugamba mutatsinda), nimwitahire. Nuko bamwe muri bo basaba umuhanuzi (Muhamadi) uburenganzira (bwo kutajya ku rugamba) bavuga bati \"Rwose ingo zacu ntawe twazisizeho\", kandi atari ko biri. Nyamara nta kindi bashakaga usibye guhunga (urugamba)"
  33,14,"N’iyo baza guterwa (n’ingabo) ziturutse mu mpande zose zawo (umujyi wa Madina), bakageragezwa basabwa (guhakana ukwemera kwabo) bari kubikora batazuyaje, ndetse nta n’abari kuwusigaramo usibye bake"
  33,15,"Ndetse rwose bari barasezeranyije Allah mbere, ko batazahunga urugamba. Kandi isezerano rya Allah bazaribazwa"